translations.name: Taverner's Bible
translations.description: Taverner's Bible, which is also called “The Most Sacred Bible whiche is the holy scripture, conteyning the old and new testament, translated into English, and newly recognized with great diligence after most faythful exemplars by Rychard Taverner,” is a minor revision of Matthew's Bible and was published in 1539.
